msgid "Updating a UCS system via UMC module 'Software update'"
msgstr ""

#: ../../software/updates.rst:45
msgid "Updating a UCS system via UMC module *Software update*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../software/updates.rst:48
msgid ""
"If a newer UCS version is available, a selection list is displayed. After"
" clicking on :guilabel:`Install release updates` and confirmation all "
"updates up to the respective version are installed. Before the "
"installation process is started, a message will be displayed informing "
"the user of possible restrictions of the server's services during the "
"update. Any intermediate versions are also installed automatically."
msgstr ""

#: ../../software/updates.rst:56
msgid ""
"Clicking on :guilabel:`Install available errata updates` installs all the"
" available errata updates for the current release and all installed "
"components."
msgstr ""

#: ../../software/updates.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Check for package updates` activates an update of the package "
"sources currently entered. This can be used, for example, if an updated "
"version is provided for a component."
msgstr ""

